title: HARRY JOWSEY SPEAKS ON NIKITA DRAGUN’S NEW SONG — BFFs EP. 49
description:
Harry Jowsey joins this week’s podcast to talk about Nikita’s new song ‘Dick’, Lil Huddy releasing his debut album, and updates on the Olivia Ponton/Kai situation. We play a game of f*ck, marry, kill and clout chaser or famous.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/bffspod
